nodes.text: A fleet of the Ishi Tib was active during the Imperial Era and was part of the government led by the high-ranking spiritual leader known as the Kalikeedan. The fleet, consisting of at least three Marsheem-class heavy cruisers, attacked and destroyed the ISD Stormbringer after the Kalikeedan decided to join the Rebel Alliance during an undercover Rebel mission to Tibrin.
